I myself conceive of the bipolarities as antithetical, not complementary, as in Taoism. In any case the defense against 3 lies in 2; in fact 2 is the route to 1. The whole campaign is to get us out of Nebelheim + into Walhalla; but Nebelheim is still here, underlying all else: forges + anvil

